  <summary date="2021-04-05T14:13:26Z" status="Introduced in House">EAGLES Act of 2021

This bill reauthorizes the National Threat Assessment Center (NTAC) within the U.S. Secret Service.

It reauthorizes the functions of NTAC through FY2025 and expands them to include the establishment of a national program on targeted school violence prevention.</summary>
